---
// Inline-authored note. The marker number is assigned client-side in
// MarkdownLayout's note script; the body is hidden until shown in the
// shared tooltip (desktop) / drawer (mobile).
---
<span class="sidenote"><button type="button" class="sidenote-ref" aria-label="Show note"></button><span class="sidenote-body" hidden><slot /></span></span>
